channel.title: [377] Map Editor
channel.description:
So I downloaded a Map Editor a few days ago, and wanted to change my mapdata. But, I figured it was meant for 317 cache, and I myself have a 377 cache. I however heard, that it was possible to edit 377 mapdata with it, by editing some ints and such.
Does anyone have a clue how to do it? This is the editor I'm talking about: https://www.dropbox.com/s/glitc39u6k0eecv/editor.rar
